@startuml View Meal Plan - Sequence Diagram

!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Peržiūrėti mitybos planą - Sequence Diagram

actor "Šeimos\nnarys" as User
participant "MealPlanningPage\n<<screen>>" as Page
participant "MealPlanningController\n<<control>>" as Controller
participant "MealPlanEntity\n<<entity>>" as MealPlan
participant "SupabaseClient\n(Core.Network)" as Supabase
database "Supabase DB\n(meal_plans)" as Database

== SCENARIJUS: Vartotojas peržiūri mitybos planą ==

User -> Page: Atidaro MealPlanningPage
activate Page

Page -> Controller: LoadMealPlanEvent(date: today)
activate Controller

note right of Controller: **BE REPOSITORY:**\nController tiesiogiai naudoja\nSupabaseClient

Controller -> Supabase: from('meal_plans')\n  .select()\n  .eq('user_id', userId)\n  .gte('plan_start_date', today)\n  .lte('plan_end_date', today)
activate Supabase

Supabase -> Database: SELECT * FROM meal_plans\nWHERE user_id = ?\nAND plan_start_date <= CURRENT_DATE\nAND plan_end_date >= CURRENT_DATE\nAND deleted_at IS NULL
activate Database

alt Planas rastas
    Database --> Supabase: MealPlan data (JSON)
    deactivate Database
    Supabase --> Controller: List<Map<String, dynamic>>
    deactivate Supabase
    
    Controller -> Controller: mapToMealPlanEntity(data)
    Controller -> MealPlan: create(data)
    activate MealPlan
    MealPlan --> Controller: MealPlanEntity
    deactivate MealPlan
    
    Controller -> Controller: processMealPlanData(mealPlan)\n- Dienos struktūra\n- Valgiai per dieną\n- Kalorijų kiekis\n- Ingredientų informacija
    
    Controller --> Page: MealPlanLoadedState(\n  mealPlan: MealPlanEntity,\n  days: [...],\n  meals: [...],\n  calories: {...}\n)
    deactivate Controller
    
    Page -> User: Rodo esamą mitybos planą:\n• Dienos (Pirmadienis, Antradienis...)\n• Valgiai per dieną\n  - Pusryčiai\n  - Pietūs\n  - Vakarienė\n• Kalorijų kiekis per valgį\n• Confidence indikatoriai\n• Ingredientų sutapimas %
    deactivate Page
    
    User -> Page: Scroll per dienas\nIšplėsti valgio detales
    activate Page
    Page -> Controller: ExpandMealEvent(day, mealType)
    activate Controller
    Controller --> Page: MealExpandedState(mealDetails)
    deactivate Controller
    Page --> User: Rodo detalų informaciją\n(ingredientai, kalorijos)
    deactivate Page

else Planas nerastas
    Database --> Supabase: null (no results)
    deactivate Database
    Supabase --> Controller: empty list
    deactivate Supabase
    
    Controller --> Page: MealPlanNotFoundState()
    deactivate Controller
    
    Page -> User: Rodo tuščią būseną:\n"Planas nerastas"\n+ Mygtukas "Generuoti planą"
    deactivate Page
endif

note over User, Database
  **SVARBU:**
  - Vartotojas tik PERŽIŪRI planą (read-only)
  - Sistema rodo visą plano informaciją
  - Vartotojas gali scroll'inti per dienas ir matyti detalius
end note

@enduml



















